001package edu.cnm.deepdive.teamle.model;
002
003import com.google.gson.annotations.Expose;
004import com.google.gson.annotations.SerializedName;
005import java.util.ArrayList;
006import java.util.List;
007
008/**
009 * Handles all league objects.
010 */
011public class League {
012
013  @Expose
014  @SerializedName("idLeague")
015  private final String id = null;
016
017  @Expose
018  @SerializedName("strSport")
019  private final String sport = null;
020
021  @Expose
022  @SerializedName("strLeague")
023  private final String name = null;
024
025  private final List<Team> teams = new ArrayList<>();
026
027  /**
028   * Gets the league ID
029   * @return String id
030   */
031  public String getId() {
032    return id;
033  }
034
035  /**
036   * gets the selected sport
037   * @return String sport
038   */
039  public String getSport() {
040    return sport;
041  }
042
043  /**
044   * Gets the league name.
045   * @return String name
046   */
047  public String getName() {
048    return name;
049  }
050
051  /**
052   * Gets all teams in selected league.
053   * @return List<Team>
054   */
055  public List<Team> getTeams() {
056    return teams;
057  }
058}
